1) Sol :

We need to create 3 seperate service file each for 1 service and 
It will be in the format .


a) [Unit]
Description=Web service
After=app-service

[Service]
<Service file configuration>

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target




b) [Unit]
Description=app service
After=db-service

[Service]
<Service file configuration>

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target


c) [Unit]
Description=db service

[Service]
<Service file configuration>

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
